Interface StataData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataSet, DataSetByteArrays, DataSetDoubleArrays, DataSetIntArrays, DataSetLongArrays, DataSetStringArrays

    public interface StataData
    Interface used to access and construct representations of Stata data set as POJOs.

    0.0.0
    Author:
    Billy Buchanan
